title: Machine Head - Burn My Eyes (Complete Edition)
description:
This is the most complete version of the Oakland based Heavy Metal band's debut album, complete with the bonus tracks from the 2003/2007 Japanese re-release and the very rare bonus disc of the 1995 Australian Tour Edition containing their 1993 demo.

All sources are taken from legit lossless sources, ripped in EAC and encoded in FLAC.

If you already have the Japanese release, feel free to download the 1993 demo, which is finally presented in lossless audio quality for the first time.

Enjoy everyone!
